Package soc.server.savegame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameLoaderJSON
    Load a game and board's current state from a JSON file into a SavedGameModel.
    GameLoaderJSON.EnumKeyedMapDeserializer<E extends java.lang.Enum<E>>
    Custom deserializer for a HashMap that has enum keys, to ignore any unknown enum constant names it may possibly contain (for forwards compatibility).
    GameSaverJSON
    Save a game and its board's current state to a JSON file.
    SavedGameModel
    Data model for a game saved to/loaded from a file.
    SavedGameModel.BoardInfo
    Board layout and contents.
    SavedGameModel.CallbackClassTypeAdapterFactory<C>
    Type adapter for GSON to serialize/deserialize a class as usual, with callbacks to change the serialized form before writing or after reading before parsing: beforeWrite(..), afterRead(..).
    SavedGameModel.Constraint
    A constraining condition requested before resuming the game.
    SavedGameModel.KnownResourceSet
    Set of the 5 known resource types, to use in saved game instead of raw 7-element int array from SOCResourceSet.
    SavedGameModel.PlayerInfo
    Info on one player position sitting in the game.
    SavedGameModel.TradeOffer
    A player's current trade offer info, from relevant fields of SOCTradeOffer and player's SOCPlayer.getCurrentOfferTime().
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SavedGameModel.UnsupportedSGMOperationException
    Details of why SavedGameModel.checkCanSave(SOCGame) or SavedGameModel.checkCanLoad(SOCGameOptionSet) or constructor can't save a game or load a model.
